name: V Nixie Hallway
description:
This is from a 2009 shoot with V Nixie. 
V has easily been one of my favorite models to shoot over the years not only because of her unique look but also because she's just plain awesome. This is my first dip into NFTs so I hope you like it and will consider adding it to your collection and coming back to see what else I have for you in the future.
